 music students at the college level and for practicing rock musicians who desire a deeper understanding of their music, this book is an essential resource.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aRock (Musique)xAnalyse et appréciation. 0aRock musicxAnalysis, appreciation. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Rock.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030012823940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300128239423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300128239/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles